font-size: 18px; color: #141933; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px\">\r\n                            Hi，亲爱的用户：\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #474C66; font-weight: 400;\">\r\n                            <strong>\$user</strong>投递了您的职位 （\$post） ，快进入平台查看简历详情吧～\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </tbody></table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n        <tr class=\" person-info\" style=\"background:#ffffff; border: 1px solid rgba(242,243,248,1); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\r\n            <td height=\"152\" style=\"padding: 6px 40px;\">\r\n                <a href=\"\$resumeUrl\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n                    <table width=\"770\" height=\"152\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"height:152px;width:770px;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;background:#fff;border: 1px solid #e8ebf3;\">\r\n                        <tbody><tr>\r\n                            <td class=\"info\">\r\n                                <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 336px;\">\r\n                                    <tbody><tr>\r\n                                        <td style=\"width:40px; height:40px\"><img src=\"\$photo_url\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" style=\"border-radius:50%; margin-right: 14px; margin-top: -30px;\"></td>\r\n                                        <td>\r\n                                            <table style=\"color: #7A8190;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n                                                <tbody><tr>\r\n                                                    <td style=\"color:#141933;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 600;\">\$user</td>\r\n                                                </tr>\r\n                                                <tr>\r\n                         